{"type":"ScenarioReference","class":"Mythos","tokens":{"front":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If you fail, resolve the Hunter keyword on a <t>Blood-Drunk</t> enemy in play."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X.  X is the number of <t>Beast</t> enemies in play. (Max 3)"},"Tablet":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If you fail, place a barricade token between your location and a connecting location."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X. Discard the top two cards of your deck.  X is the total printed cost of those discarded cards."}},"back":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. If you fail, resolve the Hunter keyword on a <t>Blood-Drunk</t> enemy in play."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X.  X is the number of <t>Beast</t> enemies in play."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-3,"description":"-3. If you fail, place a barricade token between your location and a connecting location that does not already have a barricade token."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X. Discard the top three cards of your deck.  X is the total printed cost of those discarded cards."}}},"TtsZoopGuid":"74a9825c-fdc9-43d8-b68b-842d4146611f"}
